</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lord.</SPEAKER>
<P>I believe you don't tell truth, my Lady&mdash;look up, girl&mdash;Ah Loui&s;a, Loui&s;a, that con&s;cious blu&s;h! but 'tis well you have the grace to be a&s;hamed.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Loui&s;a.</SPEAKER>
