<P>Thou prevaricating monkey&mdash;di&s;&s;emblers too from the very egg. And <HI>without</HI> my permi&s;&s;ion, Mi&s;s: what an|&s;wer does your mode&s;ty and filial piety &s;ugge&s;t to that?</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Loui&s;a.</SPEAKER>
