<P>No! Suppo&s;e the widow Knightly, with a real e&s;tate of three thou&s;and a year, and a per&s;onal one of fifty thou&s;and pounds, &s;hould have taken a fancy to you, would not that be a means?&mdash;You blu&s;h; perhaps you are already acquainted with the lady's pa&s;&s;ion.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Col.</SPEAKER>
