</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Col.</SPEAKER>
<P>My Lord, if the Lady has really done me that honour, 'tis more than I de&s;erve; for I never made the lea&s;t advances.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lord.</SPEAKER>
<P>Well; but how do you like her?</P>
