</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Sir Harry.</SPEAKER>
<P>Sweet rogue!</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lady Flutter.</SPEAKER>
<P>My dear Sir Harry!</P>
<STAGE>[He takes her hand and ki&s;&s;es it.</STAGE>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lady.</SPEAKER>
<P>Well now is not this charming?&mdash;I congratulate
