<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lady Flutter.</SPEAKER>
<P>I &s;ee his treachery. <STAGE>[A&s;ide.]</STAGE> Then, Sir Har|ry, I will convince him of his error, by making the be&s;t wife in the world, in &s;pite of him.</P>
