<P>Charming creature! I &s;hall grow too fond of you&mdash;I won't let you be &s;o engaging, hu&s;&s;y&mdash;</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lady Flutter.</SPEAKER>
<P>You &s;hall tho'&mdash;</P>
<STAGE><HI>Enter Lord</HI> Medway, <HI>who &s;tops on &s;eeing Sir</HI> Harry.</STAGE>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Sir Harry.</SPEAKER>
<P>Pray, my Lord, come in&mdash;I have a &s;ad com|plaint to make to you. This is certainly the mo&s;t perver&s;e girl!&mdash;</P>
</SP>
<SP>
