</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Sir Harry.</SPEAKER>
<P>But, my Lord, this is new, a quite &s;pick and &s;pan new affair. She has taken <HI>&s;uch</HI> a re&s;olution!</P>
</SP>
<SP>
