</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Sir Harry.</SPEAKER>
<P>You will be amazed when I tell you&mdash;We were di&s;puting about it when you came in&mdash;</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<PB N="59" REF="580">
<SPEAKER>Lord.</SPEAKER>
<P>I am &s;orry, Sir Harry, to find you always in di&s;putes with your Lady. I wi&s;h from my heart I could compo&s;e your differences&mdash;</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Sir Harry.</SPEAKER>
<P>Oh &s;he is the very &s;pirit of contradiction, my Lord.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lady Flutter.</SPEAKER>
<P>Depend upon it, Sir Harry, I will have my own way in this.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lord.</SPEAKER>
